longBusinessSummary: Focus Lighting and Fixtures Limited manufactures and deals in LED lighting, fixtures, and lighting solutions in India. It operates through two segments, Own Manufactured and Trading. The company offers recessed adjustable spotlights, recessed downlights, surface mounted spotlights, surface-mounted/suspended, system based spotlights / wall washer, track-mounted spotlights, etc. under the Plus light tech, TRIX, and Lumens & beyond under brand names. Focus Lighting and Fixtures Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Mumbai, India.
